import boy2 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/boy2.svg'

export const testimonialsData = [

        id: 1,
        name: 'Rahul',
        title: 'Sr. Manager',
        text: "Building my own portfolio could've never been easier than this. The only areas I'm good at are Math, Jokes and Dance.",

    {

        text: "Heard of the song 'Smelly Cat!!' ? This website made it viral. Plus portfolio is the only thing that Ursula doesn't have :)",

    },
    {
        id: 4,
        name: 'Ryan',
        title: 'Model',
        text:`This website not only boasts an elegant and intuitive UI design but also showcases a backend that runs like a well-oiled machine. It's a pleasure to interact with and leaves me wanting to explore more.`,

    {
        id: 5,
        name: 'Rachel',
        title: `A captivating UI that seamlessly intertwines with a powerful backend, creating an immersive and delightful user experience that keeps me coming back for more`,
